00:11:08.459 --> 00:11:10.502
locked me in his office
and assaulted me.

00:11:10.503 --> 00:11:11.920
I reported it to the police.

00:11:11.921 --> 00:11:13.672
I'm sure you have that
in your file.

00:11:13.673 --> 00:11:15.966
"Insufficient evidence."

