00:12:05.767 --> 00:12:07.435
-Can anyone confirm that?

00:12:10.313 --> 00:12:11.731
-No.

00:12:16.152 --> 00:12:17.903
-You're clear. Just need to
sign your paperwork,

00:12:17.904 --> 00:12:20.656
